    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is listed in mint condition \u2014 and we mean it. This is a truly exceptional example that stands apart from typical used car listings. The exterior is flawless, with paint that shines like new and absolutely no scratches, dents, chips, or blemishes of any kind. The interior is equally immaculate \u2014 every surface, seat, and panel looks and feels as though it just rolled off the showroom floor. Mechanically, this car is in perfect working order: all systems function exactly as intended, with no warning lights, no unusual noises, and no deferred maintenance. The tires have excellent tread depth, all glass is clear and crack-free, and the undercarriage is clean. Service records are up to date. This is the kind of vehicle that genuinely needs nothing \u2014 you can drive it away with complete confidence. Buyers who have been searching for a truly top-tier used car need look no further.",
